#: src/plugins/nonebot_plugin_lingchu_bot/handle/qq/adapters/onebot11/napcat/announcement.py:60
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"NapCat 拒绝公告图片：已发送的 image 字段为 {protocol_path}，本地缓存为 {local_path}。请检查 "
"LINGCHU_ANNOUNCEMENT_IMAGE_CACHE_DIR 与 "
"LINGCHU_ANNOUNCEMENT_IMAGE_PROTOCOL_DIR 是否一致，并确认 NapCat 容器 bind mount "
"已挂载到该路径（Windows / WSL2 部署请参考 NapCat Docker 文档）。"
msgstr ""
"NapCat rejected the announcement image: sent image field was "
"{protocol_path}, local cache is {local_path}. Check that "
"LINGCHU_ANNOUNCEMENT_IMAGE_CACHE_DIR and "
"LINGCHU_ANNOUNCEMENT_IMAGE_PROTOCOL_DIR are consistent and that the "
"NapCat container bind mount exposes that path (for Windows / WSL2 "
"deployments, see the NapCat Docker docs)."

#: src/plugins/nonebot_plugin_lingchu_bot/services/protocol_restart_feedback.py:85
msgid "协议端已重启并重新连接"
msgstr "Protocol endpoint restarted and reconnected"

#: src/plugins/nonebot_plugin_lingchu_bot/start/startup.py:59
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"公告图片缓存目录 {cache_dir} 与当前系统 {system_type} 不兼容：\n"
"当前进程在 {system_type} 上运行，但 LINGCHU_ANNOUNCEMENT_IMAGE_CACHE_DIR "
"的值带有另一操作系统（{detected_style}）的路径风格，会被 pathlib 解析为相对路径。\n"
"请按目标部署环境更新 .env 中的 LINGCHU_ANNOUNCEMENT_IMAGE_CACHE_DIR 与 "
"LINGCHU_ANNOUNCEMENT_IMAGE_PROTOCOL_DIR，并重建 NapCat 容器使 bind mount 生效。"
msgstr ""
"Announcement image cache dir {cache_dir} is incompatible with the current"
" system {system_type}:\n"
"the process is running on {system_type} but the "
"LINGCHU_ANNOUNCEMENT_IMAGE_CACHE_DIR value uses a {detected_style} path "
"style, which pathlib will resolve as a relative path.\n"
"Update LINGCHU_ANNOUNCEMENT_IMAGE_CACHE_DIR and "
"LINGCHU_ANNOUNCEMENT_IMAGE_PROTOCOL_DIR in .env for your deployment, and "
"recreate the NapCat container so its bind mount takes effect."

